import React from 'react' const Internship = () => { return (

Practical -based Online Internship in Psychology

100+ Students have already completed their internship in online mode.

Topics:

• Case history taking

• Interviewing patients

• Introduction to Intelligence and Personality Tests 

• Administration of Psychological tests 

• Scoring and interpretation of test results and diagnosis of the problem

• Psychotherapy

• Working with an interdisciplinary treatment team

• Role Play sessions and formulation of Case history, MSE, Diagnosis and Plan of Action

• Case discussion & case presentation

• Guest lectures by eminent personalities in the field of Psychology and Psychiatry

• Assistance in internship report writing

• Exposure and experience of writing blog articles, conducting research and surveys

• Regular assignments to assess the level of understanding of students and doubt solving sessions

• 10 Cases with Case History, Mental Status Examination (MSE), and Psychological Testing

) } export default Internship;
